<h1 class="postingtitle">
    <span class="postingtitletext">
<span class="price">$1,750</span> <span class="housing">/ 1br - 950ft<sup>2</sup> - </span><span id="titletextonly">Exclusive Private Guesthouse In Gated Community on Horse Farm</span><small> (Gated Community Rancho Capistrano)</small>    </span>
</h1>
<section class="userbody">
    

    <div class="mapAndAttrs">
<div class="mapbox">
    <div id="map" class="viewposting" data-latitude="33.615162" data-longitude="-117.356644" data-accuracy="5"></div>
    
    
    <p class="mapaddress">
        <small>
            (<a target="_blank" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/33.615162,-117.356644">google map</a>)
        </small>
    </p>
    
</div>

    <p class="attrgroup">



            <span class="shared-line-bubble"><b>1BR</b> / <b>1.5Ba</b></span>




             <span class="shared-line-bubble"><b>950</b>ft<sup>2</sup></span>

    </p>
    <p class="attrgroup">



            <span>air conditioning</span>
            <br>




            <span>cats are OK - purrr</span>
            <br>




            <span>dogs are OK - wooof</span>
            <br>




            <span>house</span>
            <br>




            <span>w/d in unit</span>
            <br>




            <span>no smoking</span>
            <br>




            <span>off-street parking</span>
            <br>




            <span>rent period: <b>monthly</b></span>
            <br>

    </p>
    </div>

    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="https://inlandempire.craigslist.org/apa/d/lake-elsinore-exclusive-private/7517762987.html"></div>
        </div>
Our amazing Barn House is about 950 sq ft. A loft house built into a large beautiful custom French style barn. Looks like something you would find in the European French Countryside. <br>
<br>
                    OUR WONDERFUL BARN HOUSE IS A ONE OF A KIND FARMHOUSE SANCTUARY!<br>
<br>
 *The Barnhouse is on the barns 2nd floor, it includes an office and 3rd floor loft, usually the bedroom but can be the office.<br>
<br>
The main floor includes a gorgeous custom, cooks kitchen with granite counter tops, high end appliances, antique chandelier and pantry, living room, a spacious custom bathroom and a very large office that can be the main bedroom or yoga studio.  <br>
<br>
The barn house includes antique doors, hardwood and stone floors, it's own washer, dryer as well as central AC and heating. <br>
<br>
                               The rent includes your utilities, FIOS Internet, and FIOS TV and Apple TV. <br>
<br>
            Located on a private equestrian estate in private gated community of Rancho Capistrano, nestled within the Cleveland National Forest. <br>
<br>
5 minutes from Highway 74, between Lake Elsinore and San Juan Capistrano. <br>
<br>
                                     All the amenities of city living, yet wonderful tranquil rural living. <br>
<br>
                                           A slice of heaven…. Uncommon in Southern California….<br>
<br>
Just walk out the barn door, take a hike and enjoy in the amazing natural of the Cleveland National Forest and San Mateo Wilderness, or a short 15 minutes drive to California State Park at Lake Elsinore to water ski or sail or within 45 min or less you can be on California beaches to surfing, Whale watch, sailing, swimming or just soaking in the beautiful sun.<br>
<br>
Where else can you surf in the morning, ride your horse in the afternoon and snow ski or snowboard that evening? <br>
<br>
A slice of heaven…<br>
<br>
                      If you are a horse person we are perfectly located in the center of everything equestrian! <br>
<br>
Only about 30 min East of Rancho Mission Viejo Riding Park at San Juan Capistrano, Oaks Blenheim EquiSports, 30-40 min to La Cresta (Black Dog Farm) 50 min to Ingalls Park, Norco and about 50 min to Galway Downs, Temecula. 12 min to Lake Elsinore.<br>
<br>
                             Perfect for the professional with a horse, student with a horse or a competitor with 1-2 horses that rides English (Eventer/HJ/Dressage).<br>
<br>
                                                    *1 person, or a couple, No more.* Don’t ask…<br>
<br>
<br>
                              We are open to short term rentals. People traveling with their horse or horses. <br>
<br>
HORSES<br>
<br>
The facility includes a large, custom, 8 stall barn, all In &amp; Outs, Turnout, Jumping Arena, Dressage Arena, 90’ Round Pen, W/D for horse laundry, sitting area with fireplace in barn, outside bathroom, trails + Much More.  <br>
<br>
We have a separate Quarantine area for any incoming horses to our farm, new or just returned from competition.<br>
<br>
The gated horse community of Rancho Capistrano is a horse community with private trails and direct access to the Cleveland National Forest.<br>
<br>
Horse $300/month includes dry stall and use of facility, You feed &amp; clean, Other care options are available. We provide weekly manure removal from the facility.<br>
<br>
* No, I am not a horse trainer, No I don't wish to be one, Nor do I wish to be your horse trainer.<br>
<br>
If you and your horses are used to concierge service there are people in the area you may hire. Just not me…..<br>
<br>
PETS<br>
<br>
Pets are on a case by case basis. <br>
<br>
Dogs, NO fighting or barky, nippy, destructive dogs permitted, no unaltered dogs. No Exceptions!<br>
<br>
                                                  NO!!!!NO!!!!!!!NO!!!!!!!!NO!!!!!!!!<br>
<br>
*We DO NOT offer the exchange of rent money for yard work, house work, stall cleaning, horse grooming, tea, wine or …. anything else in exchange for rent so don’t even ask.<br>
<br>
* We are not a horse rescue, people rescue, pig rescue or any other type of rescue.<br>
<br>
* No we do not allow puppy mills, chicken mills or any other mass breeding operations.<br>
<br>
* We are not your mother, your pastor your guru or your shrink.<br>
<br>
* No freaks, druggies, or drunks, you should know by now if you are....<br>
<br>
* We don't care if your straight, gay, married, single, previously married, living together, nutty... but just not nuts.<br>
<br>
THE PROCESS<br>
<br>
***Our process is similar to interviewing for a job. <br>
<br>
*****NOT first come, first in. *****<br>
<br>
This is an excellent opportunity for the right person or couple. <br>
<br>
We are quiet, easy going professionals. If you are a sensible, responsible person with a solid source of income, we would love to talk with you.<br>
<br>
*Please text or leave a message with information about yourself if you are interested. *<br>
<br>
NOTE<br>
<br>
We WILL continue to run this posting UNTIL the RIGHT tenant has been found....<br>
    </section>

